quran[5]{c,v,t}:
  113,1,"Say: \"I seek protection with/by Lord/master/owner (of) the daybreak/creation"
  113,2,From bad/evil/harm (of) what He created
  113,3,"And from bad/evil/harm (of an) intense dark night/moon, when/if (it) penetrated through body pores/ spread/approached"
  113,4,And from bad/evil/harm (of) the female magicians/sorceresses/dischargers in the knots
  113,5,"And from bad/evil/harm (of) an envious with jealousy , when/if he envied with jealousy"